  "body_html": "<!doctype html><div class=\"lake-content\" typography=\"classic\"><ol class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u5f3957eb\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">下载并安装node.js，官网地址：</span><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-cn\" data-href=\"https://nodejs.org/zh-cn\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Node.js — 在任何地方运行 JavaScript (nodejs.org)</span></a></li></ol><p id=\"u22a8a5f4\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-indent: 2em; margin-left: 2em\"><img src=\"https://file.cadengao.com/assets/doc/54197723.183049799/image/0.png\" width=\"1697.3333333333333\" id=\"u748b8125\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><p id=\"ub5568dfa\" class=\"ne-p\" style=\"text-indent: 2em\"><img src=\"https://file.cadengao.com/assets/doc/54197723.183049799/image/1.png\" width=\"622.6666666666666\" id=\"uf383f82e\" class=\"ne-image\"></p><ol start=\"2\" class=\"ne-ol\"><li id=\"u1f36b428\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">下载并安装git，官网地址：</span><a href=\"https://git-scm.com/downloads\" data-href=\"https://git-scm.com/downloads\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"ne-link\"><span class=\"ne-text\">Git - Downloads (git-scm.com)</span></a></li><li id=\"ua8cbc460\" data-lake-index-type=\"0\"><span class=\"ne-text\">用管理员打开cmd，执行</span></li></ol><span style=\"margin-left: 2em\"><pre data-language=\"csharp\" id=\"GPm5S\" class=\"ne-codeblock language-csharp\"><code>//1.检查node-v是否安装成功，成功后会提示v20.16.0\nnode -v\n//2.安装cnpm -g就是全局安装\nnpm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npmmirror.com  # -g就是全局安装\n//3.安装hexo\ncnpm install -g hexo-cli\n//4.检查hexo是否安装成功\nhexo -v</code></pre></span></div>"
